data.description: $0 DOWN PAYMENT $0 PMI for this gorgeous traditional brick front home with 2 PRIMARY BEDROOMS, 2 STORY FOYER, 2 STORY GREAT ROOM, OPEN CONCEPT, and a PRIMARY BEDROOM you've only dreamed about complete with SITTING AREA. The PRIMARY BATH has TWO PRIVATE VANITIES and a WALK IN CLOSET. This home has been meticulously maintained and loved. This low maintenance home has a NEW ROOF, NEW HOT WATER HEATER, and NEWER HVAC. The dramatic landing overlooks the 2-story foyer to receive your guests. EXTRA LARGE ROOMS, GAS COOKING & HEATING, WALK IN LAUNDRY ROOM, LEVEL YARD and more. This gorgeous home also boasts a SWIM/TENNIS, PLAYGROUND COMMUNITY. Perfectly manicured lawns throughout the neighborhood and community feel, will make this the perfect home for the next owners to love, grow and enjoy.
